  "profile": "realistic",
  "adversarial": false,
  "intent": "A realistic STIG/CIS hardened ruleset: identity + audit-config file watches, an auid-narrowed privileged execve rule, the rare time-change syscalls, and the -e 2 immutable finalize. The big realistic cost case (catalog #2).",
